GaeQuery(Class<?>, String, PageDirection, String, Map<String, Object>, Map<String, Object>, boolean) - Constructor for class com.insose.gae.pager.GaeQuery
Create a new query from a limited substet of JDOQL syntax.

query:
[[WHERE filters] [PARAMETERS parameters]] [ORDER BY orders]
filters:
filter [&& filters]
filter:
properyName operator parameterName
operator:
one of: < <= == > >=
parameters:
parameter [, parameters]
parameter:
javaTypeName parameterName
orders:
order [, orders]
order:
propertyName [ASC | DESC]
GaeQueryPager<T> - Class in com.insose.gae.pager
Generic Forward and Backward Bookmark paging for Google App Engine for Java.

At the present time, the Google App Engine does not provide a built-in pagination support.
